        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
I hate playing verant advocate becuase I grow to despise them more with each passing day but here goes anyway.

Ever heard of Dire Charm? With "zonable pets" anyone with this ability could dire the ultimate DC pet they can, in the zone of their choice and take it with them for as long as they can keep it alive.

Zones may be artificial from an RP perspective but they are an integral part of the game.

This would be overpowering for us and would lead to serious balance issues. We could essentially expend our 650 mana a single time and have a perpetual whatever high DPS spell for a single cast.

No point whining about it. It is not going to change and neither should it be.

 
[/quote]</textarea><br>
